            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the mushrooms are cooking, combine the <strong>apple matchsticks</strong>, <strong>lime juice</strong> and <strong>zest</strong> with your <strong>mayo</strong> – this is your <strong>zesty</strong> <strong>apple slaw</strong></p>",
