      "instruction": "<p>Divide the <strong>refried beans </strong>and<strong> mushrooms</strong> evenly between the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong> – these are your <strong>mushroom & refried bean tacos</strong></p><p>Garnish the tacos with the<strong> zesty apple slaw</strong> and <strong>quick-pickled red onions</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
